# 📊 Mobile Sales Analysis Dashboard

This project is a Power BI interactive dashboard created for analyzing mobile sales data across different cities and brands in India.

## ✅ Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel
- Power Query
- DAX

## 📁 Dataset
Fictional mobile sales dataset with details like:
- Brand
- Mobile model
- Sales amount
- Quantity
- Customer name
- Ratings
- Payment method
- Transaction date
- City

## 🧠 Features of the Dashboard
- KPIs: Total Sales, Total Quantity, Transactions, and Average Sales
- Time Series: Monthly quantity trends
- Region-wise Sales: Map of total sales by city
- Customer Ratings Analysis: Distribution of ratings
- Payment Method Breakdown: Pie chart
- Brand & Model Performance: Bar charts for top performers
- Weekly Insights: Sales by Day Name
- Filters for Month, Brand, Customer, and Payment Method

## 🛠️ Data Processing
- Used Power Query to clean and transform the data
- Fixed formatting and column inconsistencies directly inside Power BI
- Created custom **DAX measures** for dynamic insights

